name: Starstorm Lost
description:
Starstorm survivors that lost the poll, now finished up. 
Currently implements four survivors and two variants. Profile Flags: 

- ssl_debug: Enables several debug features, mainly a display of Brawler's input systems. 
- ssl_truebrawler: Gives default Brawler access to all special input moves. 
- ssl_heckbosses: Brawler can suplex any enemy.
author: Neik, Jingo, Altzeus
